{"tid":2048005,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門葡京酒店設紀念區讓員工公眾悼念何鴻燊","createTime":"2020-06-02T13:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T13:22:25.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f502ad9fbac0a13cbffb2608b34ef8cad7fd0cc1","tid":2048005,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529770_1_L_20200602163938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529770_1_L_20200602163938.jpg&h=aaee0afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529770_2_L_20200602163938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529770_2_L_20200602163938.jpg&h=9f03bcae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人稱「賭王」的商人何鴻燊於上星期二離世，終年98歲。澳門娛樂有限公司、信德集團以及澳博和澳博控股4間公司，今日起在葡京酒店大堂，為創辦人何鴻燊設紀念區，開放給員工和公眾致哀。<br />\n<br />\n紀念區中央放置何鴻燊的相片，兩旁用中英文字寫上「深切悼念創辦人何鴻燊博士」，下面放上白玫瑰。<br />\n<br />\n中午時，不少員工趁休班時間到紀念區簽名和三鞠躬，工作了30多年的退休員工說，夫妻兩人都屬基層員工，形容何鴻燊甚至小職員的生日都記得，曾有一次封利是給她丈夫，所以前來悼念，以表心意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529770-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529770-20200602.htm&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2Fxxgae24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=d59938db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529770-20200602.htm&h=e49ebc2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529770-20200602.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n排隊悼念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}